@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.23 * v1 + 0.94) / (v0 + 0.07 * tmp + 0.72)) * v0)
    v2 = 0.88
    v0 = (wp.exp(tmp) / wp.sin((v0 + 0.82 + v0 + 0.66)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = ((v0 * 0.68) - wp.exp((v1 + 0.87 + v2 + 0.48)))
    tmp = wp.sin(v0)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v1 + 0.72 * tmp + 0.55)))
    v0 = 0.02
    data[tid] = v0
